---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import TurkeyMap from '../components/TurkeyMap.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Bize Katil - Kampus Cadilari" description="Il il orgutlenen feminist ag ve basvuru haritasi.">
  <section class="rounded-[2rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-950 via-purple-950 to-rose-700 px-6 py-12 text-white shadow-2xl md:px-10">
    <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-fuchsia-200">Interaktif harita</p>
    <h1 class="mt-4 max-w-4xl text-4xl font-black leading-tight md:text-6xl">Her il icin tiklanabilir bilgi ve basvuru akisi tek ekranda.</h1>
    <p class="mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-white/85">
      SVG ile tasarlanmis, her ilde tiklayip ogrenilebilir daha detayli harita kisa sure icinde geliyor. Bu surumde tum iller icin etkilesimli kart yapisi ve secili il bilgi paneli hazir.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-12">
    <TurkeyMap activeProvinces={['Istanbul', 'Ankara', 'Izmir', 'Bursa', 'Gaziantep', 'Adana', 'Eskisehir', 'Mersin']} />
  </section>

  <section class="mt-12 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.95fr_1.05fr]">
    <aside class="rounded-[1.75rem] bg-white p-6 shadow-xl ring-1 ring-slate-200 md:p-8">
      <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-purple-700">Basvuru mantigi</p>
      <h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-black text-slate-900">Nasil katilirsin?</h2>
      <div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 p-4">
          <p class="font-bold text-slate-900">1. Ilini sec</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Kartlardan ilini tikla ve o ildeki durum bilgisini incele.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 p-4">
          <p class="font-bold text-slate-900">2. Rolunu belirt</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Yazi, etkinlik, il koordinasyonu, tasarim veya ceviri gibi destek alanlarini sec.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 p-4">
          <p class="font-bold text-slate-900">3. Yerel ekiple esles</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Aktif illerde mevcut ekibe, acik illerde ise kurucu gonullu havuzuna yonlendirilirsin.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <section class="rounded-[1.75rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-700 to-fuchsia-700 p-6 text-white shadow-2xl md:p-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black">Basvuru formu</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-white/85">Form simdilik on basvuru akisi olarak calisiyor. Secilen il ve rol bilgisiyle ekip size geri donus yapiyor.</p>

      <form id="join-form" class="mt-8 space-y-5">
        <div class="grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">
          <label class="block">
            <span class="mb-2 block text-sm font-bold">Ad Soyad</span>
            <input name="name" required class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-white/20 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-slate-900 outline-none ring-0" placeholder="Adinizi yazin" />
          </label>
          <label class="block">
            <span class="mb-2 block text-sm font-bold">E-posta</span>
            <input type="email" name="email" required class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-white/20 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-slate-900 outline-none ring-0" placeholder="ornek@mail.com" />
          </label>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">
          <label class="block">
            <span class="mb-2 block text-sm font-bold">Il</span>
            <input name="province" required class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-white/20 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-slate-900 outline-none ring-0" placeholder="Ornek: Izmir" />
          </label>
          <label class="block">
            <span class="mb-2 block text-sm font-bold">Rol</span>
            <select name="role" required class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-white/20 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-slate-900 outline-none ring-0">
              <option value="">Rol sec</option>
              <option>Yazi ve editorluk</option>
              <option>Etkinlik koordinasyonu</option>
              <option>Il koordinasyonu</option>
              <option>Tasarim ve gorsel uretim</option>
              <option>Ceviri ve kaynak gelistirme</option>
            </select>
          </label>
        </div>

        <label class="block">
          <span class="mb-2 block text-sm font-bold">Kisa not</span>
          <textarea name="message" rows="4" required class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-white/20 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-slate-900 outline-none ring-0" placeholder="Neden katilmak istedigini ve nasil katki sunabilecegini yaz."></textarea>
        </label>

        <button type="submit" class="w-full rounded-full bg-white px-6 py-3 font-black text-purple-700 transition hover:bg-amber-100">Basvuruyu gonder</button>
      </form>
    </section>
  </section>

  <script>
    const joinForm = document.getElementById('join-form');
    joinForm?.addEventListener('submit', (event) => {
      event.preventDefault();
      joinForm.innerHTML = `
        <div class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-white/20 bg-white/10 p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-2xl font-black">Basvurun alindi</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-white/85">Il ve rol bilgilerin kayda gecti. Ekip en kisa surede sana donus yapacak.</p>
        </div>
      `;
    });
  </script>
</MainLayout>
